name: Danpur Himalyan Rural and Agriculture Society

address: Dani Bhavan Near Mukhani Choraha Haldwani

briefDescription: Decades have passed still maximum population is leading their lives in far remote area that lack the basic need such as Environment, Education, Medical facilities, self employment. So in order to provide a platform for ensuring an all round development of the people of this region a few of them decide to have an organization. Thus came into being Danpur Himaliyan Rural and Agriculture society
